title: Update nLogLike.cpp
body: When stationary=TRUE, mle$delta in fitHMM and delta in nLogLike.cpp are not the same.  In fitHMM, mle$delta <- solve(t(diag(nbStates)-gamma+1),rep(1,nbStates)), but in nLogLike.cpp, delta = arma::solve(diag-Gamma+1,v).t().  This fix makes them the same.
